title: Haryana rice millers end strike (AIREA - All India Rice Exporters Association)
text: ( Source : AIREA - All India Rice Exporters Association ) Sensing unrelenting mood of the state government, the Haryana Rice Millers and Dealers Association (HRMDA) on Wednesday announced to end its four-day-old strike with immediate effect.
